OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the day. Dry with largely
OL,7,Fclear skies overnight, a little more
OL,8,Fcloud across southern parts. Another
OL,9,Fwarm night for many, especially in
OL,10,Furban areas and cities, while cooler
OL,11,Fin rural spots. Wind remains light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FDry and predominantly sunny to
OL,14,Fend the week. Feeling hot, with
OL,15,Fdaytime temperatures widely above
OL,16,Faverage. Cooler closer to coasts with
OL,17,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
