OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand largely sunny on Saturday, though
OL,7,Fcooler with coastal low cloud
OL,8,Flingering. Low cloud and patchy
OL,9,Fdrizzle possible early Sunday before
OL,10,Fbrightening up. Dry and sunny by
OL,11,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
